    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏机制</h2><br><br>在这个游戏中，你将操控着人如其名的「我」，想办法在文字的世界中找出生路。举例来说，当你走进一个密室时，尽管游戏内的叙述很明白地告诉你「这里没有门」，但因为这是一款文字游戏，所以你依旧可以走进叙述中的「门」，飒爽离去。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/ccd455df1e86c0cb0b155cd37183317e.poster.avif?t=1734721449\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/ccd455df1e86c0cb0b155cd37183317e.webm?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/ccd455df1e86c0cb0b155cd37183317e.mp4?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >故事介绍</h2><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/93600a03cb6ef3de10dad90a236a75ba.poster.avif?t=1734721449\" width=600 height=400 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/93600a03cb6ef3de10dad90a236a75ba.webm?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/93600a03cb6ef3de10dad90a236a75ba.mp4?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>温铎历二一零二年，魔龙入侵王都，<br>从此，便是第五大陆噩梦的开始⋯⋯<br><br>这里是勇者之村，我是新一任的勇者。<br><br>我必须先在村内通过导师们的试炼，<br>取得专属勇者的三件圣器，<br>接着，踏上讨伐魔龙的旅程⋯⋯<br><br>⋯⋯如果真有这么简单就好了。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/b45e124caddf21716d0e605f859758b8.poster.avif?t=1734721449\" width=600 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/b45e124caddf21716d0e605f859758b8.webm?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/b45e124caddf21716d0e605f859758b8.mp4?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特色</h2><br><br>「文字游戏」的核心机制就是「字」，以「字」塑造游戏世界里的谜题与人事物。不仅可以走进字面上的门，更能不断解锁各种文字能力。大胆「删字」，你可以铲除「没有门」中的「没」，让门无中生有；或者用力「推字」、果断「拆字」、精心「组字」，创造解谜的丰富变化。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/99bdb29c069f78e1433adf1fa494fc23.poster.avif?t=1734721449\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/99bdb29c069f78e1433adf1fa494fc23.webm?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/99bdb29c069f78e1433adf1fa494fc23.mp4?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/eb1e06b549b67e1799102b6900b4dd21.poster.avif?t=1734721449\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/eb1e06b549b67e1799102b6900b4dd21.webm?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/eb1e06b549b67e1799102b6900b4dd21.mp4?t=1734721449\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/extras/30aaa0c06c213405209ae355751e0cba.poster.avif?t=1734721449\" width=600 height=200 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1507970/ex